data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! Take a look this moving ready 3BR/2BA home located it in the community of Glenbrook Chase neighborhood in South Lakeland. Before the entry, you will find a small enclosed porch area. Upon entry to your right of entry is 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Both bedrooms have been upgraded with laminate flooring. Moving further into the home, you find an open floor plan with the Great Room, Dining Room, and Kitchen, perfect for entertaining! The Kitchen features a stainless appliance, breakfast bar, and a tiled backsplash. Off the Great Room is the Primary Bedroom featuring with laminate floors, ceiling fan and Suite bathroom. Boasting TWO walk-in closets, the master bathroom also includes a dual sink vanity, garden tub, and separate glass shower. Sliders from the Great Room lead to the screened back porch. Enjoy your morning coffee on the screened back porch overlooking the above ground pool, BBQs area. Fully vinyl fenced. Schedule your showing today.
